From: Arnaud Juracek <arnaud.juracek@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 21 Jul 2026 15:48:18 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 16/17] Add moderation routes: global testimony queue + status
 update

GET /testimonies/all exposes Testimonies::read_all() (previously only used
as a launch-time sanity check), and PATCH /testimony/<id> validates/censors
one. No individual staff-identity concept exists yet, so moderated_by is
attributed to a pseudo-staff row per kiosk city (src/staff.rs).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
